{{Lunar September}} '''September 29 (Old Lunar Calendar)''' is the 29th day of month {{ill|September (Old Lunar Calendar)|ja|9月 (旧暦)|lt=September}} the 9th month of the traditional {{ill|Old Lunar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Old Lunar Calendar}}. If the month is {{Nihongo|Small|小}} then this is the last day of the month. Otherwise if the month is {{Nihongo|Big|大}} then it is the second last day.{{citation needed}} It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜}} day is {{ill|Senshō|ja|先勝}}.
<!--== {{Lunar September}} ''September 29'''<!--Lunar September29 is the Nth day of [[9月 (旧暦)|Lunar September]]の29日目である。年によっては9月の最終日となる。六曜は[[六曜#先勝|先勝]][[Category:先勝]]である。
