{{Lunisolar September}} '''September 29''' is the 29th day of month {{ill|September (Lunisolar)|ja|9月 (旧暦)|lt=September|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the 9th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . If the month is {{Nihongo|Small|小}} , then this is the last day of the month; if the month is {{Nihongo|Big|大}} , then it is the second-last day.<ref>https://web.archive.org/web/20250111081847/https://www.chinaknowledge.de/History/Terms/calendar.html</ref><ref>https://www.nippon.com/en/japan-glances/jg00122/the-japanese-calendar.html</ref> Its Rokuyō is {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and its day is {{ill|Senshō|ja|先勝|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} .
== Events == * {{ill|Tenpyō|ja|Tenpyō|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 19th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|747|ja|747|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 6|ja|11月6日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – The casting of the giant Buddha at Tōdai-ji began. * {{ill|Kennin|ja|建仁|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd year（{{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1203|ja|1203|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 4|ja|11月4日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – Regent {{ill|Hōjō Tokimasa|ja|北条時政|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} confined Shogun {{ill|Minamoto no Yoriie|ja|源頼家|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} to Izu ({{Izu Shūzenji}} ). * {{ill|Tenwa (Japan)|ja|天和|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1681|ja|1681|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 9|ja|11月9日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – Due to the Xinyou Revolution, the era name was changed from {{ill|Enpō|ja|延宝|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} to {{ill|Tenwa|ja|天和|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} .
