== Births == * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 8th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1837|ja|1837|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 28|ja|10月28日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Tokugawa Yoshinobu|ja|徳川慶喜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the 15th shōgun of the Edo Shogunate († {{ill|1913|ja|1913|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 14th year（閏9月）（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1843|ja|1843|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 20|ja|11月20日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Shinagawa Yajirō|ja|品川弥二郎|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a Chōshū retainer and politician († {{ill|1900|ja|1900|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Bunkyū|ja|文久|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1862|ja|1862|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 20|ja|11月20日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Kuroiwa Ruika|ja|黒岩涙香|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a journalist and novelist († {{ill|1920|ja|1920|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Keiō|ja|慶応|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong