== Events == * {{ill|Tenpyō|ja|Tenpyō|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 19th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|747|ja|747|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 6|ja|11月6日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – The casting of the giant Buddha at Tōdai-ji began. * {{ill|Kennin|ja|建仁|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1203|ja|1203|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 4|ja|11月4日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – Regent {{ill|Hōjō Tokimasa|ja|北条時政|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} confined Shogun {{ill|Minamoto no Yoriie|ja|源頼家|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} to Izu ({{Izu Shūzenji}} ). * {{ill|Tenwa (Japan)|ja|天和|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1681|ja|1681|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 9|ja|11月9日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – Due to the Xinyou Revolution, the era name was changed from {{ill|Enpō|ja|延宝|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} to {{ill|Tenwa|ja|天和|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} .
== Births == * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 8th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1837|ja|1837|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 28|ja|10月28日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Tokugawa Yoshinobu|ja|徳川慶喜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the 15th shōgun of the Edo Shogunate († {{ill|1913|ja|1913|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 14th year（閏9月）（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1843|ja|1843|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 20|ja|11月20日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Shinagawa Yajirō|ja|品川弥二郎|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a Chōshū retainer and politician († {{ill|1900|ja|1900|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Bunkyū|ja|文久|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1862|ja|1862|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 20|ja|11月20日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Kuroiwa Ruika|ja|黒岩涙香|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a journalist and novelist († {{ill|1920|ja|1920|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Keiō|ja|慶応|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1865|ja|1865|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 17|ja|11月17日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Uchida Yasuya|ja|内田康哉|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a diplomat and politician († {{ill|1936|ja|1936|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
