{{Lunisolar September}} '''September 29''' is the 29th day of month {{ill|September (Lunisolar)|ja|9月 (旧暦)|lt=September (Nagatsuki)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , the 9th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft}} . If the month is {{Nihongo|Small|小}} , then this is the last day of the month; if the month is {{Nihongo|Big|大}} , then it is the second-last day.<ref>https://web.archive.org/web/20250111081847/https://www.chinaknowledge.de/History/Terms/calendar.html</ref><ref>https://www.nippon.com/en/japan-glances/jg00122/the-japanese-calendar.html</ref> Its Rokuyō is {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=draft|qq=draft}} and its day is {{ill|Senshō|ja|先勝|qq=draft|qq=draft}} .
== Events == * {{ill|Tenpyō|ja|Tenpyō|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 19th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|747|ja|747|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|November 6|ja|11月6日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） – The casting of the giant Buddha at Tōdai-ji began. * {{ill|Kennin|ja|建仁|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 3rd year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|1203|ja|1203|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|November 4|ja|11月4日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） – Regent {{ill|Hōjō Tokimasa|ja|北条時政|qq=draft|qq=draft}} confined Shogun {{ill|Minamoto no Yoriie|ja|源頼家|qq=draft|qq=draft}} to Izu ({{Izu Shūzenji}} ). * {{ill|Tenwa (Japan)|ja|天和|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|1681|ja|1681|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|November 9|ja|11月9日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） – Due to the Xinyou Revolution, the era name was changed from {{ill|Enpō|ja|延宝|qq=draft|qq=draft}} to {{ill|Tenwa|ja|天和|qq=draft|qq=draft}} .
== Births == * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 8th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|1837|ja|1837|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|October 28|ja|10月28日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） – {{ill|Tokugawa Yoshinobu|ja|徳川慶喜|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , the 15th shōgun of the Edo Shogunate († {{ill|1913|ja|1913|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 14th year（閏9月）（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|1843|ja|1843|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|November 20|ja|11月20日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） – {{ill|Shinagawa Yajirō|ja|品川弥二郎|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , a Chōshū retainer and politician († {{ill|1900|ja|1900|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ). * {{ill|Bunkyū|ja|文久|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 2nd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|1862|ja|1862|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|November 20|ja|11月20日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） – {{ill|Kuroiwa Ruika|ja|黒岩涙香|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , a journalist and novelist († {{ill|1920|ja|1920|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ). * {{ill|Keiō|ja|慶応|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|1865|ja|1865|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|November 17|ja|11月17日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） – {{ill|Uchida Yasuya|ja|内田康哉|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , a diplomat and politician († {{ill|1936|ja|1936|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Enchō (era)|ja|延長|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 8th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|930|ja|930|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|October 23|ja|10月23日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） – Emperor {{ill|Daigo|ja|醍醐天皇|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , in his 60s (* {{ill|885|ja|885|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ). * {{ill|Tenryaku|ja|天暦|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 3rd year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|949|ja|949|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|October 23|ja|10月23日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） – Emperor {{ill|Yōsei|ja|陽成天皇|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , the 57th emperor (* {{ill|868|ja|868|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ). * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 2nd year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|1574|ja|1574|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|October 13|ja|10月13日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） – {{ill|Oda Nobuhide|ja|織田信広|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , a military commander. * {{ill|Shōtoku (Japan)|ja|正徳|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 2nd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|1712|ja|1712|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|October 29|ja|10月29日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） – {{ill|Yanagihara Sukenori|ja|柳原資廉|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , a court noble (* {{ill|1644|ja|1644|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ). * {{ill|Kyōwa|ja|享和|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|1801|ja|1801|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|November 5|ja|11月5日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） – {{ill|Motoori Norinaga|ja|本居宣長|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , a kokugakusha (* {{ill|1730|ja|1730|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ).
