== Events == * {{ill|Tenpyō|ja|Tenpyō|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 19th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|747|ja|747|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|November 6|ja|11月6日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ） – The casting of the giant Buddha at Tōdai-ji began. * {{ill|Kennin|ja|建仁|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 3rd year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1203|ja|1203|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|November 4|ja|11月4日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ） – Regent {{ill|Hōjō Tokimasa|ja|北条時政|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} confined Shogun {{ill|Minamoto no Yoriie|ja|源頼家|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} to Izu ({{Izu Shūzenji|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Tenwa (Japan)|ja|天和|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 1st year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1681|ja|1681|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|November 9|ja|11月9日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ） – Due to the Xinyou Revolution, the era name was changed from {{ill|Enpō|ja|延宝|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} to {{ill|Tenwa|ja|天和|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} .
== Births == * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 8th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1837|ja|1837|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 28|ja|10月28日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Tokugawa Yoshinobu|ja|徳川慶喜|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , the 15th shōgun of the Edo Shogunate († {{ill|1913|ja|1913|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 14th year（閏9月）（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1843|ja|1843|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|November 20|ja|11月20日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Shinagawa Yajirō|ja|品川弥二郎|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , a Chōshū retainer and politician († {{ill|1900|ja|1900|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Bunkyū|ja|文久|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 2nd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1862|ja|1862|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|November 20|ja|11月20日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Kuroiwa Ruika|ja|黒岩涙香|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , a journalist and novelist († {{ill|1920|ja|1920|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Keiō|ja|慶応|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 1st year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1865|ja|1865|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|November 17|ja|11月17日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Uchida Yasuya|ja|内田康哉|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , a diplomat and politician († {{ill