{{afc comment|1=This article as with the other date articles is relatively limited in scope to Japan. Reviewing the translation of this is good and also adding content translated from Chinese and Korean wikipedias will also be good. Both wikipedias are also relatively centered around their own countries for their Lunisolar calendar dates[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 00:17, 28 April 2025 (UTC)}} {{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=九月廿九|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=음력 9월 29일|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar September|qq=}} '''September 29''' is the 29th day of month {{ill|September (Lunisolar)|ja|9月 (旧暦)|lt=September (Nagatsuki)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/September (Lunisolar)|qq=}} , the 9th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} . If the month is {{Nihongo|Small|小|qq=}} , then this is the last day of the month; if the month is {{Nihongo|Big|大|qq=}} , then it is the second-last day.<ref>https://web.archive.org/web/20250111081847/https://www.chinaknowledge.de/History/Terms/calendar.html</ref><ref>https://www.nippon.com/en/japan-glances/jg00122/the-japanese-calendar.html</ref> Its Rokuyō is {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyō|qq=}} and its day is {{ill|Senshō|ja|先勝|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Senshō|qq=}} .
== Events == * {{ill|Tenpyō|ja|Tenpyō|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenpyō|qq=}} 19th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|747|ja|747|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/747|qq=}} {{ill|November 6|ja|11月6日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 6|qq=}} ） – The casting of the giant Buddha at Tōdai-ji began. * {{ill|Kennin|ja|建仁|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kennin|qq=}} 3rd year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1203|ja|1203|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1203|qq=}} {{ill|November 4|ja|11月4日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 4|qq=}} ） – Regent {{ill|Hōjō Tokimasa|ja|北条時政|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hōjō Tokimasa|qq=}} confined Shogun {{ill|Minamoto no Yoriie|ja|源頼家|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Minamoto no Yoriie|qq=}} to Izu ({{Izu Shūzenji|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Tenwa (Japan)|ja|天和|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenwa (Japan)|qq=}} 1st year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1681|ja|1681|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1681|qq=}} {{ill|November 9|ja|11月9日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 9|qq=}} ） – Due to the Xinyou Revolution, the era name was changed from {{ill|Enpō|ja|延宝|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Enpō|qq=}} to {{ill|Tenwa|ja|天和|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenwa|qq=}} .
== Births == * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenpō|qq=}} 8th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1837|ja|1837|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1837|qq=}} {{ill|October 28|ja|10月28日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 28|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Tokugawa Yoshinobu|ja|徳川慶喜|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokugawa Yoshinobu|qq=}} , the 15th shōgun of the Edo Shogunate († {{ill|1913|ja|1913|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1913|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenpō|qq=}} 14th year（閏9月）（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1843|ja|1843|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1843|qq=}} {{ill|November 20|ja|11月20日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 20|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Shinagawa Yajirō|ja|品川弥二郎|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shinagawa Yajirō|qq=}} , a Chōshū retainer and politician († {{ill|1900|ja|1900|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1900|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Bunkyū|ja|文久|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bunkyū|qq=}} 2nd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1862|ja|1862|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1862|qq=}} {{ill|November 20|ja|11月20日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 20|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Kuroiwa Ruika|ja|黒岩涙香|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kuroiwa Ruika|qq=}} , a journalist and novelist († {{ill|1920|ja|1920|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1920|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Keiō|ja|慶応|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keiō|qq=}} 1st year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1865|ja|1865|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1865|qq=}} {{ill|November 17|ja|11月17日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 17|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Uchida Yasuya|ja|内田康哉|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Uchida Yasuya|qq=}} , a diplomat and politician († {{ill|1936|ja|1936|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1936|qq=}} ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Enchō (era)|ja|延長|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Enchō (era)|qq=}} 8th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|930|ja|930|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/930|qq=}} {{ill|October 23|ja|10月23日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 23|qq=}} ） – Emperor {{ill|Daigo|ja|醍醐天皇|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Daigo|qq=}} , in his 60s (* {{ill|885|ja|885|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/885|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Tenryaku|ja|天暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenryaku|qq=}} 3rd year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|949|ja|949|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/949|qq=}} {{ill|October 23|ja|10月23日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 23|qq=}} ） – Emperor {{ill|Yōsei|ja|陽成天皇|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yōsei|qq=}} , the 57th emperor (* {{ill|868|ja|868|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/868|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenshō|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenshō (Momoyama period)|qq=}} 2nd year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1574|ja|1574|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1574|qq=}} {{ill|October 13|ja|10月13日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 13|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Oda Nobuhide|ja|織田信広|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Oda Nobuhide|qq=}} , a military commander. * {{ill|Shōtoku (Japan)|ja|正徳|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shōtoku (Japan)|qq=}} 2nd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1712|ja|1712|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1712|qq=}} {{ill|October 29|ja|10月29日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 29|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Yanagihara Sukenori|ja|柳原資廉|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yanagihara Sukenori|qq=}} , a court noble (* {{ill|1644|ja|1644|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1644|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Kyōwa|ja|享和|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kyōwa|qq=}} 1st year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1801|ja|1801|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1801|qq=}} {{ill|November 5|ja|11月5日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 5|qq=}} ） – {{i