рь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1574|ja|1574|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1574|qq=}} {{ill|October 13|ja|10月13日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 13|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Oda Nobuhide|ja|織田信広|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Oda Nobuhide|qq=}} , a military commander. * {{ill|Shōtoku (Japan)|ja|正徳|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shōtoku (Japan)|qq=}} 2nd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1712|ja|1712|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1712|qq=}} {{ill|October 29|ja|10月29日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 29|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Yanagihara Sukenori|ja|柳原資廉|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yanagihara Sukenori|qq=}} , a court noble (* {{ill|1644|ja|1644|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1644|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Kyōwa|ja|享和|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kyōwa|qq=}} 1st year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1801|ja|1801|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1801|qq=}} {{ill|November 5|ja|11月5日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 5|qq=}} ） – {{i