== Births == * [[:en:Tenpō|Tenpō]] 8th year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1837|ja|1837|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1837|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} [[:en:October 28|October 28]] ） – [[:en:Tokugawa Yoshinobu|Tokugawa Yoshinobu]] , the 15th shōgun of the Edo Shogunate († {{ill|1913|ja|1913|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1913|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 1000}} ). * [[:en:Tenpō|Tenpō]] 14th year（閏9月）（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1843|ja|1843|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1843|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 1000}} [[:en:November 20|November 20]] ） – [[:en:Shinagawa Yajirō|Shinagawa Yajirō]] , a Chōshū retainer and politician († {{ill|1900|ja|1900|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1900|qq=}} ). * [[:en:Bunkyū|Bunkyū]] 2nd year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1862|ja|1862|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1862|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} [[:en:November 20|November 20]] ） – [[:en:Kuroiwa Shūroku|Kuroiwa Ruika]] , a journalist and novelist († {{ill|1920|ja|1920|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1920|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 1000}} ). * [[:en:Keiō|Keiō]] 1st year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1865|ja|1865|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1865|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} [[:en:November 17|November 17]] ） – [[:en:Uchida Kōsai|Uchida Yasuya]] , a diplomat and politician († {{ill|1936|ja|1936|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1936|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 1000}} ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Enchō (era)|ja|延長|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Enchō (era)|qq=}} 8th year（[[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] {{ill|930|ja|930|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/930|qq=|comment=enwiki is a redirect}} [[:en:October 23|October 23]] ） – Emperor [[:en:Emperor Daigo|Daigo]] , in his 60s (* {{ill|885|ja|885|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/885|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} ). * [[:en:Tenryaku|Tenryaku]] 3rd year（[[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] {{ill|949|ja|949|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/949|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 900}} [[:en:October 23|October 23]] ） – Emperor [[:en:Emperor Yōzei|Yōsei]] , the 57th emperor (* {{ill|868|ja|868|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/868|qq=|comment=enwiki is a redirect}} ). * [[:en:Tenshō (Momoyama period)|Tenshō Era]] 2nd year（[[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1574|1574]] [[:en:October 13|October 13]] ） – [[:en:Oda Nobuhiro|Oda Nobuhide]] , a military commander. * [[:en:正德|Shōtoku (Japan)]] 2nd year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1712|ja|1712|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1712|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} [[:en:October 29|October 29]] ） – {{ill|Yanagihara Sukenori|ja|柳原資廉|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yanagihara Sukenori|qq=}} , a court noble (* {{ill|1644|ja|1644|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1644|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} ). * [[:en:Kyōwa|Kyōwa]] 1st year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1801|ja|1801|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1801|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 1800}} [[:en:November 5|November 5]] ） – [[:en:Motoori Norinaga|Motoori Norinaga]] , a kokugakusha (* {{ill|1730|ja|1730|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1730|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} ).
